    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1900-05-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1900-05-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="582"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d582">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Cambon</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the French Republic</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-05-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 3, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The President of the French Republic has just
                    heard of the terrible catastrophe which has taken place at Salt Lake City. He
                    has instructed me to be his interpreter near the President of the United States
                    of America and to assure him of the sympathy which he feels on account of this
                    sad event.</p>
                <p>In transmitting to me the expression of the sentiments of President Loubet,
                    Minister Delcassé, minister of foreign affairs, likewise instructs me to convey
                    to the American Government the expression of the profound sympathy of the
                    Government of the Republic.</p>
                <p>Be pleased to accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jules Gambon.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
